				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It's worth nothing that for all practical purposes in your emulator, you can treat <em>everything</em> as unsigned.  The only thing that must be signed is the relative address for branching.
<br />
<br />The 'N' flag just means 'high bit set'.  Therefore values $80-$FF will set N, and values $00-7F will clear N.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

